text: Paige Tapp (born 21 June 1995) is an American volleyball player. She played at the 2017 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, and 2018 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup. She played for the University of Minnesota's women's volleyball team.
